{"tid":1053524,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"有啲戥小肥唔抵","createTime":"2019-03-09T06:39:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T04:28:01.000Z","uid":208536,"like":14,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e2a2110d1e7afa1970898c97bc5f392ad613dcf3","tid":1053524,"uid":208536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:39:36.000Z","msg":"平時都無乜點留意有乜歌手<br />\n有咩新歌咁<br />\n多數搭車聽下歌<br />\n岩岩聽到小肥隻時光機<br />\n可能有共鳴啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽得特別入神<br />\n上utube搵下佢有咩歌<br />\n搵到佢年幾前係大台唱個隻寵物<br />\n真係好Q好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下因乜事佢紅唔起<br />\n啲人成日話佢樣柒<br />\n乜佢真係樣衰到依個地步咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋 個樣柒真係好影響到佢紅唔紅得去？<br />\n同埋見佢啲新聞好似都無咩負面野<br />\n全能既連登仔有咩睇法<br />\n利申非打手<br />\n淨係聽既佢隻負親 同時光機"},{"pid":"10b852b0fd01d7fec4edcb5e016ebee217a29d7f","tid":1053524,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:41:01.000Z","msg":"紅過一排啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5450be126e959848e365af6ae05cf8bb953d1f1","tid":1053524,"uid":63877,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:42:09.000Z","msg":"首寵物幾多年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主00後?"},{"pid":"c6b919351b7d93acd70796ea92248ee5d6fed591","tid":1053524,"uid":208536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5450be126e959848e365af6ae05cf8bb953d1f1","tid":1053524,"uid":63877,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:42:09.000Z","msg":"首寵物幾多年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主00後?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:43:34.000Z","msg":"前排上大台唱同以前唱既好似唔同左咁<br />\n以前聽到淨係覺得都係啲mk歌無咩特別<br />\n可佬佢越老越有男人味<br />\n聽到好滄桑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b759cc892a6a19f1ed96a718fa04d3f59d07ff2f","tid":1053524,"uid":208536,"like":0,"disli